{
  "id": "5d1d6c1f23c1300017d18ccc",
  "title": "やりがい搾取",
  "created": 1562209315,
  "updated": 1562210957,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5d1d6c1f23c1300017d18ccc",
      "text": "やりがい搾取",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209315,
      "updated": 1562209316
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6c24aff09e00005ea7f3",
      "text": "\tAさんがBさんに価値Xを提供する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209316,
      "updated": 1562209351
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6c47aff09e00005ea7f5",
      "text": "\tBさんがAさんに対価Yを提供する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209351,
      "updated": 1562209362
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6c52aff09e00005ea7f6",
      "text": "\tAさんはこの活動にやりがいを感じている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209362,
      "updated": 1562209435
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6c9aaff09e00005ea7f8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209435,
      "updated": 1562209435
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6c9baff09e00005ea7f9",
      "text": "この状況で",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209435,
      "updated": 1562209438
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6c9daff09e00005ea7fa",
      "text": "\t第三者Cさんが「対価Yが価値Xに対して少ない」と感じた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209438,
      "updated": 1562209488
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6cd3aff09e00005ea7fb",
      "text": "の場合に、Cさんはこれを「やりがい搾取」と呼ぶことがある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209491,
      "updated": 1562209503
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6cdfaff09e00005ea7fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209503,
      "updated": 1562209503
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d6cdfaff09e00005ea7fd",
      "text": "「やりがい搾取」という言葉は不必要に強く感情を刺激する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562209503,
      "updated": 1562210628
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d7112aff09e00005ea7fe",
      "text": " 「対価Yが価値Xに対して少ない」は第三者Cさんの主観",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562210579,
      "updated": 1562210833
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d7147aff09e00005ea7ff",
      "text": " \t主観に基づいて「損な取引だ」と思ってるに過ぎない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562210631,
      "updated": 1562210833
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d716daff09e00005ea800",
      "text": " 「やりがい搾取」というラベルを貼ることによって客観的な事実が存在するかのような誤解を生む。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562210669,
      "updated": 1562210834
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d720baff09e00005ea803",
      "text": " \t「Bさんは悪である」が事実であるかのようなバイアスを生む",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562210828,
      "updated": 1562210899
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d721faff09e00005ea805",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562210848,
      "updated": 1562210932
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d71dfaff09e00005ea801",
      "text": "[不適切な抽象化]だと思うので「具体的に何が問題であるか」を掘り下げる方が良いと思う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562210784,
      "updated": 1562210957
    },
    {
      "id": "5d1d71e6aff09e00005ea802",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1562210790,
      "updated": 1562210790
    }
  ]
}